name: Experiment Or Die #109
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Any of my adolescent crushes were on women in movies or television. I had a thing for Gina Davis from A League of Their Own (1992), Elisabeth Shue from The Saint (1997), but noone was sexier than Jessica Rabbit from Who Framed Roger Rabbit (1988). She was animated but lets be honest, animated or not, she's a bombshell. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
